function to evaluate models¶

In [102]:
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, f1_score
def evaluator(pred):
    print(f"accuracy score: {accuracy_score(y_test, pred)}")
    print(f"f1 score: {f1_score(y_test, pred, average = 'weighted')}")
